// Menace = a block-arrangement cardinality bound [CR#702.111b]: "can't be
// blocked except by two or more creatures" — a Cant(Block) row whose
// CountBound forbids arrangements with fewer than two blockers (the
// comparator-headed set-level constraint this grammar was built for).
KeywordAbility(
    name: "Menace",
    template: "menace",
    abilities: [Static(effects: [
        Cant(Block(on: Ref(This), count: Less(Literal(2)))),
    ])],
)
